Download Nodejs from any browser

Backend ChatApp -CMD =>
	Open the backend folder in visual studio code
		- npm init -y
		- npm i express
		- npm i socket.io
		- npm i nodemon   // It automatically restarting the node application when file changes

To config nodemon at backend
		- backend folder - package.json file
			 "scripts": {
    				"start": "nodemon index.js",
  			},
		//Add the above line in package.json file

  To run the backend
      npx node index.js

Frontend ChatApp - CMD =>
	Open the frontend folder inn visual studio code
		- npx create-react-app .
		- npm install react-router-dom
		- npm i socket.io-client
		- npm install sweetalert2

	To use fontawesome use these command
			= npm install --save @fortawesome/react-fontawesome
			= npm install --save @fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons
			= npm install --save @fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core

	To use tailwind-CSS in frontend folder
		- npm install -D tailwindcss
		- npx tailwindcss init

		- Add the below line in tailwind.config.js file
			content: [
    				"./src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}",   //Add this line in tailwind.config.js
  		],

		- Add the below line in index.css
			@tailwind base;       
			@tailwind components;
			@tailwind utilities;

To run the frontend 
		- npm run start  
